<br>
The description of Nexus Gate that Verant provides in the &quot;Alt.Adv.Exp screen&quot; in-game, is as follows:<br>
<br>
Nexus Gate<br>
Type: Activated, Refresh Time: 72 mins.<br>
Requirements: Level 59, must spend 12 ability points in the Archetype Abilities.<br>
This ability gives you an instant-cast self gate spell to the Nexus.<br>
<br>
<br>
Now we know that the spell is NOT instant-cast, instead, it is 1.0 seconds cast time. The difference is obvious, you may be interrupted when casting the spell in its current state (which means you lose the ability to recast for 72minutes), and you cannot use this spell while running, etc.<br>
<br>
So, take your best shot! What do YOU predict Verant's response will be?<br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
